---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Southbank Centre · Project | Surrey Contracting Limited"
  description="Case study, surfacing and external works at the Southbank Centre, delivered by Surrey Contracting Limited."
  path="/project-southbank-centre"
  ogTitle="Southbank Centre Project | Surrey Contracting Limited"
  active="projects"
>

<section class="proj-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="page-hero-img" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/surfacing.jpg')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-vignette"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container proj-hero-inner">
    <nav class="crumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      <a href="/projects">Projects</a>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      <span>Southbank Centre</span>
    </nav>
    <span class="proj-hero-tag">Commercial · Surfacing</span>
    <h1 class="page-title">Southbank Centre</h1>
    <p class="page-lede">External works and surfacing programme delivered around live cultural-venue operations on London's Southbank.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container proj-detail-grid">
    <aside class="proj-meta-card">
      <h4>Project info</h4>
      <dl class="proj-meta-list">
        <div><dt>Client</dt><dd>Southbank Centre</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Location</dt><dd>London SE1</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Sector</dt><dd>Commercial / Public Realm</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Services</dt><dd>Surfacing · Groundworks · Drainage</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Duration</dt><dd>14 weeks</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Status</dt><dd><span class="proj-status">Completed</span></dd></div>
      </dl>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-yellow btn-block">Discuss a similar project →</a>
    </aside>

    <div class="proj-body">
      <h2>The brief</h2>
      <p>Surrey Contracting was engaged to deliver a phased external works programme at the Southbank Centre, one of the UK's busiest cultural venues, without disruption to public access or live programming.</p>
      <p>Works included surface-water drainage upgrades, full-depth surfacing reconstruction in two adjacent service yards, and the reinstatement of pedestrian footways and crossings. Logistics were planned around evening performances and weekend public access, with night-shift surfacing pours used to keep the site open through the day.</p>

      <h2>The delivery</h2>
      <p>Excavation and base reconstruction were completed in 50-metre bays over a 6-week programme, with binder and surface courses laid on phased weekends. Pedestrian routes were maintained throughout with temporary tactile crossings and signed diversions.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>2,400m² of full-depth reconstruction</li>
        <li>180lm of precast kerbing and channel</li>
        <li>320m of new surface-water drainage and gullies</li>
        <li>Phased delivery around live venue operations</li>
        <li>Full traffic-management and pedestrian-route maintenance</li>
        <li>Independent core sampling and compliance testing on completion</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>The outcome</h2>
      <p>Handover was achieved on programme with zero impact on ticketed performances. The new surfaces and drainage have improved both accessibility and run-off capacity, and the Southbank Centre's facilities team have since commissioned us for follow-on works.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section page-section-grey">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">On site</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">In progress &amp; on completion.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="proj-gallery">
      <div class="proj-thumb proj-thumb-lg" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/surfacing.jpg')"><span class="ph-label">Surfacing, base course</span></div>
      <div class="proj-thumb" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/bulk-earthworks.jpg')"><span class="ph-label">Reduce dig</span></div>
      <div class="proj-thumb" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/paving.jpg')"><span class="ph-label">Reinstated footway</span></div>
      <div class="proj-thumb" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/brickwork.jpeg')"><span class="ph-label">Drainage chambers</span></div>
      <div class="proj-thumb" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/block-paving.jpeg')"><span class="ph-label">Block-paved bays</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head split">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">More projects</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">See another case study.</h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-outline-dark">All projects →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-grid">
      <article class="gallery-card">
        <a href="/projects" class="gallery-link">
          <div class="gallery-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/bulk-earthworks.jpg')"><span class="gallery-tag">Groundworks</span></div>
          <div class="gallery-body">
            <span class="gallery-meta">Residential · Guildford</span>
            <h3>Phase 2, Stoke Park</h3>
            <span class="gallery-cta">View project →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </article>
      <article class="gallery-card">
        <a href="/projects" class="gallery-link">
          <div class="gallery-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/hard-landscaping.jpg')"><span class="gallery-tag">Surfacing</span></div>
          <div class="gallery-body">
            <span class="gallery-meta">Residential · Cobham</span>
            <h3>The Long Drive</h3>
            <span class="gallery-cta">View project →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </article>
      <article class="gallery-card">
        <a href="/projects" class="gallery-link">
          <div class="gallery-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/paving.jpg')"><span class="gallery-tag">Surfacing</span></div>
          <div class="gallery-body">
            <span class="gallery-meta">Schools · Epsom</span>
            <h3>Sixth-form courtyard</h3>
            <span class="gallery-cta">View project →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
